---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../config';
---

<Layout title={`Privacy Policy - ${siteConfig.title}`} description="How we protect your privacy, trust, and personal information">
  <section class="py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent via-blue-50 to-transparent">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Your Privacy Is Sacred To Us</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8">
        At SouledFolks, we understand that trust is foundational to healing. Your personal information is protected 
        with the utmost care and respect.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

      <div class="space-y-12">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🔐 Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Your confidentiality is not just a legal obligation—it's a sacred responsibility. Every piece of information you share 
            with us is protected with industry-leading security measures and deep respect for your autonomy and dignity.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">📋 What Information We Collect</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We only collect information that helps us serve you better:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mr-3">•</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Your name, email, and phone number—only when you choose to share it</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mr-3">•</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Message Content:</strong> Whatever you share in our contact form, treated with complete confidentiality</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold mr-3">•</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Minimal analytics to help us improve our website—not to track you</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">💙 How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Your information is used exclusively to:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mr-3">✓</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Respond to your messages with genuine care and attention</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mr-3">✓</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Connect you with the right support resources</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mr-3">✓</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Improve our services based on your feedback</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-indigo-600 font-bold mr-3">✓</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Comply with legal requirements that keep us accountable</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            We will <strong>never</strong> sell, trade, or share your information with third parties for marketing purposes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-50 to-indigo-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-blue-200">
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🛡️ How We Protect Your Data</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold mr-3">🔒</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Encryption:</strong> All data is encrypted both in transit and at rest</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold mr-3">🔒</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Secure Servers:</strong> Hosted with trusted providers using enterprise-grade security</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold mr-3">🔒</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Limited Access:</strong> Only authorized team members access your information</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-teal-600 font-bold mr-3">🔒</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Regular Audits:</strong> We continuously monitor our security practices</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🍪 Cookies & Tracking</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            We use minimal cookies to improve your browsing experience. These are not used to track you across the web 
            or build a profile of your behavior. You can disable cookies in your browser settings at any time.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">🔗 Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            Our website may link to external resources. We're not responsible for their privacy practices. 
            We recommend reviewing their policies before sharing any information with them.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">✋ Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Your information, your control. You have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold mr-3">→</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Access and review your personal data anytime</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold mr-3">→</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Request corrections if information is inaccurate</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold mr-3">→</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Request deletion of your data (with exceptions for legal requirements)</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-purple-600 font-bold mr-3">→</span>
              <span class="text-gray-700">Opt out of any non-essential communications</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">📝 Policy Updates</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this policy periodically to reflect our practices. Significant changes will be posted here 
            with an updated date. We'll also make reasonable efforts to notify you directly if changes affect your privacy.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">📧 Questions? We're Here</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have questions or concerns about how we handle your information, please don't hesitate to reach out:
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 mb-6">
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900">Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.email}`} class="text-blue-600 hover:text-indigo-600">{siteConfig.email}</a></li>
            <li><strong class="text-gray-900">Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${siteConfig.phone}`} class="text-blue-600 hover:text-indigo-600">{siteConfig.phone}</a></li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-indigo-50 to-cyan-50 p-8 rounded-lg border border-indigo-200">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">💜 Our Privacy Pledge</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            At SouledFolks, protecting your privacy is more than compliance—it's a core value. Your trust is 
            everything to us, and we take that responsibility seriously. We will always be transparent about how 
            we use your information and give you control over your data.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
